collection.name: ALPACADABRAZ 3D
collection.description:
This is our 3D Collection - to visit our Genesis Collection [click here](https://opensea.io/collection/alpacadabraz)

3D Pacas are your ticket to the upcoming "PacaVerse." Whether you enjoy Esports, Play-to-Earn games or simply socializing in the Metaverse, your Pacas provide you that access.


By performing well on our upcoming games, you can earn traits that can be used with your existing 3D Paca. And Pacas are also mountable, so your other 3D avatars can literally ride on your Paca while cruising through the Sandbox!

We’ve only scratched the surface and there’s a lot more in store. The team is working with the best Sandbox developers to bring Paca users a unique and innovative experience within and beyond our own Sandbox land. Stay tuned.
